headline: CONAGRA BRANDS REAFFIRMS FISCAL 2026 GUIDANCE AHEAD OF 2026 CAGNY PRESENTATION
summary: In a presentation tomorrow at the 2026 Consumer Analyst Group of New York (CAGNY) conference, Conagra Brands Inc. (NYSE: CAG) will present information on its business strategies and financial outlook. Conagra will also preview a series of new innovations expected to launch in calendar year 2026.
